response.original_title: The Found Footage Festival Presents "Zany" Zingers and Bonked-Out Blunders
response.overview: "Zany" Zingers and Bonked-Out Blunders* is Found Footage Festival's release of over 50 of the most laff-tacular videos from the Foundfootagefest.com vaults. It's a laff-stravaganza of the weird, wonderful and just plain wacky world of found videos.
response.tagline: Over 50 VHS gems from The Found Footage Festival archives.
response.title: The Found Footage Festival Presents "Zany" Zingers and Bonked-Out Blunders
